               <head>Lata’if al-tava’if by Safi</head>
               <msContents>
                  <summary><title>Laṭāʾif al-ṭavāʾif</title>, a collection of Sufi, religious, historical and morally edifying anecdotes and tales by the Timurid litterateur by ʿAlī ibn Ḥusayn Vāʿiẓ Kāshifī Ṣafī</summary>
                  <msItem class="http://lccn.loc.gov/sh2006003807 http://lccn.loc.gov/sh2002009961" n="1" xml:id="Uk_Delhi_Persian_1206A-item1">
                     <textLang mainLang="fa" otherLangs="ar">Persian and Arabic</textLang>
                     <note>
                        <p>Written after a year-long siege of Hirāt (Herat) in praise of a Naṣīr al-Dīn Ẓahīr al-Millah Shāh Muḥammad Sulṭān, and in a simple prose style with poetry for the delight of his élite and common contemporaries.</p>
                        <p>The work comprises fourteen chapters termed bāb.</p>
                        <p>Dated colophon (f. 225r): completed in the city of Kashmīr (Srinagar), 18 Rabīʿ al-S̲ānī 1141/21 November 1728.</p>
                        <p>Scribal nastaʿlīq tending to shikastah āmīz by multiple hands; irregular use of naskh for Arabic passages or rubrics.</p>
                        <p>Annotations in margins.</p>
                        <p>Stamped foliation.</p>
                        <p>Lacking original binding.</p>
                        <p>Paper dust wrapper (BEIC legal publication on Regulation II for 12 February 1819, 2 Phagun 1225 Banglah era, 2 Phagun 1226 faṣlī era, 3 Phagun 1226 Vilāyatī era, 2 Phagun 1875 samvat era, 16 Rabīʿ al-S̲ānī 1234 hijrī era); torn and stained.</p>
                        <p>Folios unbound, stains, wormholes.</p>
                        <p>Condition fragile.</p>
                     </note>
                     <title xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" key="work_5080">Laṭāʾif al-ṭavāʾif</title>
                     <title xml:lang="fa" key="work_5080">لطائف الطوائف</title>
                     <author>
                        <persName xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" key="ark:/81055/vdc_100164658925.0x000001 viaf_90077852">ʿAlī ibn Ḥusayn Vāʿiẓ al-Kāshifī Ṣafī</persName>
                        <persName xml:lang="fa" key="viaf_90077852">على بن حسين واعظ كاشفى صفى</persName>
                     </author>
